MINH BOUTIQUE - TROPICAL FOREST We are Minh Boutique located in heart of Da Nang. With unique architecture, covered by green trees, green space, and fresh air. We are a best choice for relax. Whoever you are, visit Minh Boutique to listen peacefully your soul.
