Anny R wrote a review Feb 2024
Singapore, Singapore60 contributions4 helpful votes
+1
Just like home
Sweet boutique hotel. Lovely decor. Very clean. Excellent team running the place, very helpful. Amazing breakfast!!! So much to try of the local cuisine. Just like at home haha because we can hear our neighbours, the clitter clatter of the staff preparing breakfast. Not too disturbing though but just expect silence. The cock will crow at dawn too!
