Mrudvi wrote a review Dec 2023
4 contributions3 helpful votes
Good but misses out on a few basics
While the boutique hotel looks beautiful it lacks the basic amenities. Bathroom is extremely small and surprisingly they have the wash basin outside the bathroom- something I’ve never seen. The hot water barely runs for 7-8 minutes before getting completely cold. On the plus side the staff is very cordial and helpful.
Date of stay: December 2023
