Frequently Asked Questions about Minh Boutique
Which popular attractions are close to Minh Boutique?
Nearby attractions include Sky 21 Bar (0.2 miles), Phuoc My Beach (0.2 miles), and Mystery Bar & Lounge (0.07 miles).
See all nearby attractions.
What are some of the property amenities at Minh Boutique?
Some of the more popular amenities offered include free wifi, free breakfast, and a pool.
See all property amenities.
Which room amenities are available at Minh Boutique?
Top room amenities include a kitchenette, a minibar, and air conditioning.
See all room amenities.
What food & drink options are available at Minh Boutique?
Guests can enjoy free breakfast, an on-site restaurant, and a lounge during their stay.
Learn more.
Is parking available at Minh Boutique?
Yes, free parking is available to guests.
What are some restaurants close to Minh Boutique?
Conveniently located restaurants include Nem Restaurant, Sky View Restaurant, and My Casa Tapas Bar.
See all nearby restaurants.
Are there opportunities to exercise at Minh Boutique?
Yes, guests have access to a pool during their stay.
Does Minh Boutique have airport transportation?
Yes, Minh Boutique offers airport transportation for guests. We recommend calling ahead to confirm details.
Are any cleaning services offered at Minh Boutique?
Yes, dry cleaning and laundry service are offered to guests.
Which languages are spoken by the staff at Minh Boutique?
The staff speaks multiple languages, including English and Vietnamese.
